---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
---

<Container>
  <div
    class='relative flex flex-col-reverse items-center md:flex-row'
    id='hero'>
    <div class='row items-center py-5 md:w-6/12 md:pb-20 md:pt-10'>
      <div class='text-left space-y-3'>
        <h1 class='text-5xl font-medium leading-none md:text-6xl'>
          Changing the <br /> way you perfect <bold>your speaking experience,</bold>
          <br /> and automate day2day with AI
          
        </h1>
        <p class='mt-6 mb-8 text-xl font-normal leading-7 sm:mb-12'>
            Our voice-to-voice simulator, powered by machine learning, is designed to enhance your speaking fluency. It offers a broad array of exercises and simultaneous sessions that can extend for hours, providing ample practice for improvement.
        </p>
        <a
          class='px-9 py-5 bg-zinc-900 hover:bg-white text-white hover:text-black border rounded-2xl justify-items-center md:justify-items-start gap-2.5 inline-flex'
          rel='noopener noreferrer'
          href='https://github.com/manulthanura/Positivus'
          target='_blank'>
          <h2 class='text-center text-xl font-normal leading-7'>
            Want to try it?
          </h2>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='flex items-center py-5 md:w-6/12 md:pb-20 md:pt-10'>
      <img src='/Hero.svg' width='100%' alt='Hero' />
    </div>
  </div>

